<h2 id="head">Head and Face</h2><p><strong>头 (tóu)</strong> head, <strong>眼睛 (yǎnjing)</strong> eyes, <strong>耳朵 (ěrduo)</strong> ears, <strong>鼻子 (bízi)</strong> nose, <strong>嘴巴 (zuǐba)</strong> mouth, <strong>牙齿 (yáchǐ)</strong> teeth, <strong>头发 (tóufa)</strong> hair.</p>
    <h2 id="body">Body</h2><p><strong>手 (shǒu)</strong> hand, <strong>脚 (jiǎo)</strong> foot, <strong>腿 (tuǐ)</strong> leg, <strong>胳膊 (gēbo)</strong> arm, <strong>肚子 (dùzi)</strong> stomach, <strong>背 (bèi)</strong> back, <strong>心 (xīn)</strong> heart.</p>
    <h2 id="health">Health Phrases</h2><p><strong>我头疼 (wǒ tóu téng)</strong> I have a headache. <strong>我肚子疼 (wǒ dùzi téng)</strong> I have a stomachache. Practice writing these characters with our <a href="/chinese/tools/practice-sheet/">Practice Sheet Generator</a>.</p>
